Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Guess you're stuck\Nhere for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check up on\Nyou tomorrow, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NIs that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- [HILING sighs]\N- [KAGE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NNo... She wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING grunts, groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE chuckles]\NThe moon is pretty tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[humming]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] Still skulking\Nabout inside the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] Then you've\Nforfeited your opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now read the will\Nof the late king.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The successor to the throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANDEO]\N...is to be Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[GROUP gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DORSHE] What's that?\N- [gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping, yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[DEMON 3A]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[GROUP gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain this, Magic Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NPrince Daida. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's been\Nchosen to become king!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Yet the\Nthrone shall belong to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all proceeding in full\Naccordance with my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSPEOPLE murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 3A sighs]\NSo First Prince Bojji's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,really gonna become\Nour next king?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel safer with\NPrince Daida on the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By will of the late King Bosse,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we hereby announce\Nhis successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[SORII]\NYour new king...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...is Prince Daida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasps]\N- [TOWNSPEOPLE cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] This cannot stand.\NI move to veto the king's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasping]\N- But― Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd defy his wishes and keep\NPrince Bojji from the throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you truly believe Bojji is\Ncapable of serving as king?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The will though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To simply disregard\Nthe late king's mandate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After what we witnessed\Non his deathbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,how could we follow his will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] The seven of us\Nshall vote to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the successor to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, eyes closed\Nand hands forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever believes Bojji is\Ncapable of serving as king,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,raise up your finger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NOpen your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us are opposed\Nto his succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By a vote of five to two,\NDaida shall become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Domas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSPEOPLE cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 3A gasps]\NPrince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[wails]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay... outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NNo time to hurt. Gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] It takes a great deal\Nof grit to carve through
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your own flesh,\Nand I commend you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly... I can't let you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] Now, who sent\Nyou to this castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and who did they want killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your last chance.\NAnswer now or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] I told you before,\NI'm not here to kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanna do is help\NBojji any way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To help Prince Bojji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the creature\NI've drawn here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NYou call him a friend? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend has sent me\Nto deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He has just set off\Non a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He said you will never\Nbe seeing each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I came\Nhere to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,By your leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Listen.\NI'm on your side, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He has set off on a journey.\NYou won't see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Aeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NYou've summoned me, King Daida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stand atop\Nthe Ranking of Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, I must\Neliminate any unstable elements
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,within my court.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apeas and Sandeo were the ones\Nwho voted against me, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN gasps]\NHow could you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] Hmph. Please,\Ngive me a bit of credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want those two disposed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead men tell no tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] I doubt this was\NKing Daida's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What seeds has that Magic Mirror\Nbeen planting in his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[GATEKEEPER 3B]\NPrince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aeh! Aeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been far too long,\NPrince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Master Bebin, has\Napprehended the creature
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you now seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NA-eh! Ah, eh, eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never forgotten\Nthe debt which I owe you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet, even for your sake,\NI cannot ignore the debt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe to my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu! Au-au-eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[MITSUMATA] Prince Boji,\Nyour friend is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He and Master Bebin\Narranged a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He has gone off on a journey\Nto fulfill an important duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I can say no more\Nof this to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can offer you an assurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are held precious\Nin the sight of so many,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and you must not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NEuah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[MITSUMATA]\NNow, please run along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather Master Bebin\Nnot learn of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you acting on\NKing Daida's orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS]\NTch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- [APEAS grunts]\N- [BEBIN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN rasping]\NKing Daida...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS] I will see\NPrince Bojji become king...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] You asked Apeas\Nand Sandeo to resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] The Spear of\Nthe King is not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have Bebin\Nin my service,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm told that you and Sandeo\Nhave found yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,at odds lately, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] Even so, I worry\Nthat you've acted in haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is to be done\Nabout Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"What is to be done"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This matter is giving me\Nrather a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] Ideally, we could\Nhave him retired to―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentally speaking,\NPrince Bojji is only a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an obligation\Nto educate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA groans] That could be a\Nmiserable experience for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain he would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need\Nto trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the king\Nand should act as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHmph. Wise words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall heed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[DEMON 3A mumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NBojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NPreposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Au! Ah-ooh-eeh! Au! Au-eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no such journey.\NI won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you can\Ndo under your own power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] Your ears are deaf\Nand your body is frail,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and you embarrass yourself every\Ntime you step out in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to stay put in\Nthe castle and behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the king's older brother,\Nand thus―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a duty to the\Nroyal family and to Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpers softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NWha― Ah! Bu―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji, on direct\Norders from Queen Hiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we are not to let you\Nleave your chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-eh. Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji? I'm coming in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gone mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Dorshe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Au! Eh! Augh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!\NAre you trying to get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NBojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING gulping]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasps]\N- [BOJJI] Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Au, au, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSCHE]\NStay with me, Queen Hiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAIDS giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be a miserable\Nexperience for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hiling.\NIt's so lovely to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting now,\NI'm going to be your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, the prince hasn't\Nopened his heart to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,since the late queen's passing,\Nso it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NI see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Prince.\NWhat have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some... cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI babbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Prince, you're dripping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NMm? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [HILING snarls]\N- Ah? Au, au!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh, eh! Au! Au-au! Yeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Au, au! Au!\N- Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAID 3C] Prince Bojji has\Nbeen growing quite attached
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to the young queen\Nlately, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji. Before long, you're going\Nto become a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NSee? You felt it move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's hardly a need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, this boy\Nis not fit to be a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall permit you\Nto take your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah--!\N- However!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be accompanied by two\Nothers. One is the Swordmaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Domas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name, if you would?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hokuro! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one soldier who wished\Nto join you, and he can sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hokuro will tend to\Nyour personal care
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,during your travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall see\Nmy family at their home
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and offer your respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will\Npromptly return here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand what\NI'm saying, then respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [BOJJI] Mwah.\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Enough dawdling! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE]\NQueen Hiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING] What was that?\NThat sense of foreboding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreboding, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A sudden sensation\Nas if they're lost to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Bojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Daida.
